<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-37-0739 </DOCNO><TEXT>The Fast Gas Injection Facility (SGI) was set up to study the hydrodynamicsduring the expansion of a gas bubble into a vessel filled with water.The gas stored in a pressure vessel expands against gravity through acircular duct into a large cylindrical vessel partly with water. Thisreport covers the description of the test facility and the data acquisition.Results of the first test series are added.</TEXT></DOC>